Izuku: I HAVE A QUESTION ABOUT YOUR QUIRK!!!

Shouji: *running away in a panic*

Izuku: *chasing after him and screaming* SO ABOUT YOUR QUIRK! WHAT DO YOU DO WITH YOUR TEETH? YOU CAN CREATE MOUTHS ON THE ENDS OF YOUR DUPLI-ARMS SO DO THOSE TEETH EXIST SOMEWHERE INSIDE YOU OR DO YOU MAKE NEW TEETH EVERY TIME YOU MAKE A MOUTH? AND IF THEY ARE PRE EXISTING DO YOU HAVE TO BRUSH THE TEETH IN EACH MOUTH EVERY NIGHT? IF YOU EAT SOMETHING WITH A DUPLI-MOUTH DOES IT GO TO YOUR STOMACH? HOW OFTEN DO YOU-

Shouji: *sobbing* sTOp ASkiNG mE QueStiONS!!!
